{"tid":595898,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★最低工資的雙職二人家庭，已超出入息上限，喪失申請公屋資格","createTime":"2018-03-17T06:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T05:30:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9d671d205e6348537d32ab3a0c5841e76e117237","tid":595898,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】房屋委員會即將檢討公屋入息和資產限額，惟現行機制下，賺取最低工資的雙職二人家庭，已因收入「高」超出入息上限，喪失申請資格，備受詬病。不過，房屋署堅持毋須將公屋入息限額與最低工資住戶收入比較，拒絕檢討；立法會議員尹兆堅批評房署以行政手段壓縮基層住屋需求，<span style=\"color: red;\">連清潔工、保安員都申請不到公屋</span>，實在諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n房署文件稱，有意見認為一個賺取最低工資每小時三十四元五角的雙職二人家庭，每人每日工作十小時、每月工作廿六日，每月家庭入息已超逾建議的二人家庭公屋入息限額一萬七千六百元，不合資格申請公屋，指按照現行機制計算所得的公屋入息限額偏低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180317/00176_091.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180317%2F00176_091.html&d=fZM7N6QrlwatQABWD2VYM0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=b702efd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180317/00176_091.html</a>"},{"pid":"2dedd01ca6ee2c7f070112b304ee24f42458b4e0","tid":595898,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ae1bd7da64a7f4038fc1f90d52875b6b383d9e","tid":595898,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:32:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">返工=No公屋</span>"},{"pid":"652618a7d021b730f6930e4876ee62a033067c9e","tid":595898,"uid":3241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"可以諗下申請到果班人渣係點申請到"},{"pid":"41ef78828b26fc4f5463dd9d6b78101bbcfe91e8","tid":595898,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedB